---
title: Parmesan Pan-Fried Chicken Gnocchi with Spinach and Peas
description: Golden, pan-fried gnocchi add a delicious twist to classic Alfredo! Rich cream and savoury Parmesan come together to make a luscious sauce for this supper.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220530_R1018_W29_CA_RV0473-3_KB_Main_low-d6e968bb.jpg
